14 personnel officers who administer the personnel systems under KRS Chapter 151B
15 and KRS Chapter 18A shall exercise the necessary administrative procedures to
16 effect the change in personnel authority. No certified or equivalent employee in the
17 Department for Adult Education and Literacy shall suffer any penalty in the
18 transfer.
